high_descs: Turn around to exit the room on the right and head down the passage on the left to reach the living room on the left and face the shelf under the tvstand.
Pick up the glass bowl from the tray.
Walk straight and turn right at the passage to the end of it to turn right and walk into the bedroom and reach the dresser on the left.
Put the bowl on the dresser.
Turn around to exit the room and walk down the passage to reach the living room coffeetable.
Pick up the bowl next to the apple from the table.
Walk straight to the passage and turn right to the end of the passage and reach the dresser on the left of the bed.
Put the bowl on the dresser to the right of the other bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put two bowls on the dresser.

high_descs: Leave the room take a left and go to the tvstand on the left.
Pick up the clear bowl on the stand.
Go forward and take a right into the hallway and a right into the room and go to the dresser.
Put the bowl on the dresser.
Leave the room take a left and then the left into the living room go to the coffeetable.
Pick up the clear bowl on the table that is the bowl farthest from the kitchen.
Go forward take a right and then a right into the bedroom and go to the dresser.
Put the bowl on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Place two bowls on the dresser.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the tv stand on your right.
Pick up bowl from the tv stand.
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the dresser.
Place bowl on the tv stand.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the coffee table.
Pick up bowl from the tv stand.
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the dresser.
Place bowl on the tv stand.
anns.task_desc: Collecting bowl from different places and arranging them on a tv stand.
